Currently the bulk watch only possible if the user has the Bulk Change permission in Global Permission. However, this means that a user which don't have the Bulk Change permission doesn't able to perform bulk watch in JIRA at all.

h5. Suggestion:
Create a separate permission for Bulk Watch feature so that administrator can have a better control on the feature and grant to a suitable list of users. In addition, this can prevent user who have bulk change permission to execute more sensitive action such as bulk change.

